  "texts": [
    "The reasoning abilities that enable autonomous planning and execution of analytical tasks [9]- [11], while code generation capability support creating insightful visualizations efficiently [12]- [14].",
    "Additionally, their broad knowledge base makes LLMs versatile tools capable of adapting to diverse data analysis contexts [15], [16].",
    "LEVA [17] integrates LLMs in VA systems to recommend insights for a given task but still cannot generate visualization and data modeling methods adapted to tasks.",
    "There is a lack of approaches supporting task planning, VA methods implementation, and interactive analysis with human-agent collaboration.This paper introduces LightVA, a lightweight VA framework with agent-based task planning.",
    "The term \"lightweight\" refers to the framework's focus on reducing the cost of development and using VA systems."
